last_episode_to_air.name: The Banana Peel (2)
last_episode_to_air.overview: Nate and Malika help Ben, the banana peel, get his powers back, but he betrays them. Instead of using his powers to become human, he takes revenge on humanity by turning the town into a magic realm! As magical creatures invade the city, our heroes try to help.

name: Nate Is Late
overview: Every morning, Nate and Malika leave home 30 minutes early to go to school, and yet every morning they arrive late! That’s because every morning, something AMAZING happens on the way. But even though their stories are always true, Principal Prudence never believes them…

episodes.name: The Garbage Goblins
episodes.overview: As Nate shows Malika the watch he got for his birthday, he drops it down a sewer grate! The kids head into the sewers to get it back, but it's been picked up by a goblin.

episodes.name: The Roman Ruins
episodes.overview: The way to school is blocked by a construction site. Nate and Malika decide to go through it to save time, but they end up in the ruins of an ancient Roman amphitheatre.

episodes.name: The Carnivorous Plant
episodes.overview: Nate has forgotten to take care of the class' carnivorous plant over the weekend. He and Malika try to restore the plant's luster but it turns it into a giant monster!

episodes.name: The Dragon
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika notice some burnt bushes, leading them to a baby dragon! It looks like his mother abandoned him, so Nate decides to adopt him - but raising a dragon is not easy!

episodes.name: The Insects
episodes.overview: Professor Toybos is putting his latest invention in the bin. It's a shrink ray, but it doesn't work... Nate plays with the controls and accidentally gets him and Malika shrunk.

episodes.name: The Secret Agent
episodes.overview: On the way to school, Nate and Malika bump into a strange man who claims to be an undercover secret agent.

episodes.name: The Leprechaun
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet a leprechaun in the park. His name is Shaun and he's lost his pot of gold. Nate and Malika must help Shaun to find it or he will be turned to stone.

episodes.name: The Adorable Monster
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika are offered a free ride on a ghost train which turns out to be a cover to train young monsters.

episodes.name: The Haunted House
episodes.overview: Melanie gives Nate and Malika a letter to be delivered to an old mansion. The mailbox is full, so our heroes enter the house to give the letter to the resident in person.

episodes.name: The Enchanted Frog
episodes.overview: On the way to school, Nate and Malika meet Gideon, a young man turned into a frog by a witch. Nate tries kissing him to reverse the curse, but it transforms him too!

episodes.name: The Kid From The Future
episodes.overview: Nate accidentally drops his biscuit packet in the park’s lake. As he goes to get it, he hears a beautiful song coming from the waters… and falls in the lake!

episodes.name: The Mermaids
episodes.overview: Nate accidentally drops his biscuit packet in the park’s lake. As he goes to get it, he hears a beautiful song coming from the waters… and falls in the lake!

episodes.name: The Genie
episodes.overview: Melanie the mailwoman entrusts Nate and Malika with a parcel to deliver. Nate discovers it contains an oil lamp. He rubs it and a genie comes out, ready to grant Nate three wishes

episodes.name: The Magic Book
episodes.overview: Nate accidentally drops his biscuit packet in the park’s lake. As he goes to get it, he hears a beautiful song coming from the waters… and falls in the lake!

episodes.name: The Sorcerer's Apprentice
episodes.overview: On the way to school, Nate and Malika meet Winkle, a sixth century sorcerer's apprentice who has accidentally sent himself into the 21st century.

episodes.name: The Cuddly Toy
episodes.overview: Nate accidentally drops his biscuit packet in the park’s lake. As he goes to get it, he hears a beautiful song coming from the waters… and falls in the lake!

episodes.name: The Superhero
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika are attacked by little gooey creatures. Luckily, Miracle Girl saves them. But the attack was a trap devised by her nemesis, Gigantix, to catch her.

episodes.name: The Alien
episodes.overview: A spaceship lands in the park! Nate and Malika meet Zediak, an alien who is running away from space pirates. Nate and Malika want to help him, until they learn Zediak's real story.

episodes.name: The Robot
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet Elvex, Professor Toybos' robot assistant. Elvex has rebelled against the professor and plans to take control of all the electrical devices in town.

episodes.name: Santa's Reindeer
episodes.overview: It’s almost Christmas, and Nate and Malika meet Santa Claus in the park. He lost his favourite reindeer as he was taking him for a test ride. It turns out the reindeer has been kidnapped.

episodes.name: The Pocket Watch
episodes.overview: Nate’s parents give him his great-grandfather’s watch to help him be on time. As he shows it to Malika, Nate activates a mysterious mechanism that traps them in a time loop.

episodes.name: The Cyborgs
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika discover that some of the people they see every morning are actually cyborgs with a human appearance.

episodes.name: The Mummy
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika sneak into a museum so they can have a private viewing of the mummy of an ancient Egyptian girl-queen.

episodes.name: Grandpa
episodes.overview: A small shooting star crash lands in front of Nate and Malika. She is being chased by another star who wants to absorb her light.

episodes.name: The Candy Factory
episodes.overview: When Nate and Malika visit a new sweet shop, Nate is so delighted by the sweets that he wants to know how the shopkeeper made them.

episodes.name: The Tree People
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika find Violet weeping next to an old tree that's going to be cut down. They discover there's a world inside the tree and must help save it.

episodes.name: The Lucky Ring
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet a construction worker who gives Nate a magical lucky ring. As soon as he puts the ring on, Nate has incredibly good luck!

episodes.name: The Faun
episodes.overview: When Nate and Malika notice the faun statue in the park is missing, they follow hoof prints into a clearing where a bunch of fauns are having a giant party!

episodes.name: The Ninja
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet Jin, a ninja who offers to train them. In order to become a master, he needs to prove he has students. Curious to see a real secret dojo, the kids agree.

episodes.name: The Battle of the Gods
episodes.overview: A storm strikes the neighbourhood and Nate and Malika discover its cause: the Greek gods Zeus and Poseidon are arguing over who deserves to rule over Mount Olympus.

episodes.name: The Totems
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika are surprised to come across Mrs Rainfort, Maurice and Violette all in bad moods. What could be bothering everyone?

episodes.name: The Gingerbread Man
episodes.overview: On the way to school, Nate and Malika save a talking Gingerbread Man from a cat. But the little biscuit boy isn't very grateful.

episodes.name: The Cave Girl
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet a girl named Oona who is from the Stone Age! Oona accidentally slipped into our time period through a portal opened by Professor Toybos.

episodes.name: The Flash
episodes.overview: Cosmo gets rid of his old photography equipment. Nate recovers an antique camera fitted with an enormous flash!

episodes.name: The Werewolf
episodes.overview: A huge beast has ransacked Cosmo's kiosk. Nate and Malika investigate and find out the beast is actually a young woman who happens to be a werewolf

episodes.name: The Gremlins
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika come across a pair of gremlins who are planning a prank that will engulf the city in sewage. Our heroes must turn the tables on the pranksters to save the city.

episodes.name: The Dinosaur
episodes.overview: Professor Toybos invents a spray that turns animals into dinosaurs. Nate accidentally squirts Maurice with the dinosaur DNA, turning the boy into a T-Rex.

episodes.name: The Concert
episodes.overview: Malika's favourite singer is doing a charity concert in the park, but his voice is stolen. When Nate confronts him, his own voice is replaced by chicken sounds.

episodes.name: The Snow Fairy
episodes.overview: Nate finds a snow globe containing a fairy figurine. He accidentally breaks the snow globe and frees the fairy, who starts to turn everyone into ice statues!

episodes.name: The Unicorn
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika discover that a unicorn living in the park is able to control minds with his horn, so uses it on Nate and Malika to make them do his bidding.

episodes.name: The Invaders (1)
episodes.overview: It's the last day of school and our heroes make a point of arriving on time. Prudence can't believe it, but then she's sucked up by a tractor beam.

episodes.name: The Invaders (2)
episodes.overview: Earth is about to be invaded by aliens through an intergalactic portal! Can our heroes defeat them?

episodes.name: The Lady of the Lake
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet a lady who was turned into water centuries ago by an ancient curse, and is trapped in the lake for eternity. To free her, they have to complete a magic ritual.

episodes.name: The Thunderbird
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika run into an ornithologist who's trying to prove the existence of the legendary thunderbird! She attracts one to the neighbourhood, but it's captured by Maxime Dermy.

episodes.name: The Crocodile Man
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet a reporter investigating a crocodile-man hiding in the town's sewers. Things get complicated when a real crocodile appears.

episodes.name: The Golem
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet Easter, an alchemist chasing the clay Golem she created. Nate and Malika have to save it from the alchemist, who wants to destroy her creature!

episodes.name: The Hairdresser
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet a hairdresser with a spray that makes people's hair grow really fast. But when his own hair starts growing uncontrollably it threatens to engulf the whole town.

episodes.name: The Mood Enhancer
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika discover that a crazy inventor has decided to eradicate bad moods by altering everyone's brains against their will. Nate and Malika have to stop him.

episodes.name: The Chess Game
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika discover an old chess set in Cosmo's shop - but as Malika tries to teach Nate the rules, the pieces start to grow and restart their centuries-old fight.

episodes.name: The Drone
episodes.overview: Pedro, a shady businessman, is winning over the inhabitants with his super-sophisticated delivery drone, but Nate and Malika find out that he's stealing his goods from Cosmo's shop.

episodes.name: The Astronaut
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet Cleo, an astronaut who has been ejected from the space station where she works with her fellow researcher Bobby. To help, our heroes embark on a space mission.

episodes.name: The Gorgon
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet Stheno, a gorgon sculptor who can turn people into stone with her third eye! She turns Maurice into a sculpture for her exhibition at the museum.

episodes.name: The Dimensional Rift
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika go their separate ways to school. Nate comes across Professor Toybos being chased by a rival scientist, who locks him up in a dimensional rift… and Nate with him!

episodes.name: The Reptilians
episodes.overview: Suzaris, a reptilian who emerged from a fault line in the ground, wants to bring proof of the surface’s existence back to her home - but the rift she opened is causing earthquakes!

episodes.name: The Enchanted Bracelet
episodes.overview: A rain of stones is threatening to wreck Nate and Malika’s neighbourhood, because there’s a war going on in the kingdom of giants, up above the clouds!

episodes.name: The Ink Thief
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet Joanna, a famous novelist who has writer’s block, so uses a magic pen to write for her! But for the pen to work, she has to feed it texts.

episodes.name: The Tiki
episodes.overview: The town receives a gift from Polynesia: a Tiki, a sacred volcanic stone statue. But suddenly the Tiki comes to life and threatens to unleash its devastating power on the city!

episodes.name: The Puppet
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika come across Garett, a ventriloquist’s magical puppet, who pranks unsuspecting people. Nate is a huge fan of Garett’s, but he and Malika soon find his pranks hurtful.

episodes.name: The Mandrake
episodes.overview: As Nate and Malika gather plants in the park to fill the herbarium for a school assignment, Nate mistakenly unearths a mandrake.

episodes.name: The Vampires
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika meet Winifred, a friendly vampire. His classmate Harmony has evil intentions, and soon our heroes have to face a blood-thirsty vampire queen returning from limbo!

episodes.name: The Greek Sphinx
episodes.overview: In the town’s Roman ruins, Nate and Malika discover a secret passage which leads them to a Sphinx! She offers them legendary treasure if they can answer her riddles correctly.

episodes.name: The Pendulum
episodes.overview: Malika falls under the spell of a magic pendulum held by Marvo the hypnotist. Under his influence, she steals a precious diamond from the museum and gives it to Marvo!

episodes.name: The Giant Koi
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika row a boat across the lake and get swallowed by a giant fish! Inside the fish, they find Maxime Dermy, the unscrupulous animal trafficker who was swallowed too!

episodes.name: The Wedding Dress
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika stumble upon a magic wedding dress that’s bringing clothes to life - and the wedding dress falls in love with Nate’s new bow-tie, dragging him along!

episodes.name: The Household Spirit
episodes.overview: A poltergeist moves into Malika’s house and starts wrecking it! Only Malika’s 'home spirit' can get rid of it, but it was living in the bread bin that she just threw away.

episodes.name: The Great Pili-Pala
episodes.overview: Tako, a squid-man, wants to free the Great Pili Pala, an ancient monster. Nate and Malika must stop the Great Pili-Pala before it makes the water rise and floods the entire city!

episodes.name: The Never Ending Recess
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika arrive at school on time! They can enjoy the morning recess for once. But while playing hopscotch, they awake Tricksy, a strange spirit dressed like a Harlequin.

episodes.name: Police Fowl
episodes.overview: A robot policeman with a chicken head replaces Policeman Dwayne! Depressed, Dwayne decides to retire. But soon, the Chicken Cop malfunctions and starts wreaking havoc in the city!

episodes.name: The Kitsune
episodes.overview: Kitsu, a young Japanese Kitsune, is stealing food and causing mayhem in town. When the fox swallows the eye of the Jade Dragon's statue, it awakens the wrath of the dragon spirit who threatens to destroy the town!

episodes.name: The Collector
episodes.overview: Nils, a collector of magic game cards, turns Melanie, the town postwoman, into a character in his game! In order to free her, Nate and Malika have to challenge him.

episodes.name: The Kappa
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika rescue a kappa, a creature who lives in the park's pond. The creature believes it has to repay them a debt of honour, so it tries helping them - but it just makes everything worse!

episodes.name: The Magic Bean
episodes.overview: A rain of stones is threatening to wreck Nate and Malika's neighbourhood because there's a war going on in the kingdom of giants, up above the clouds! To stop the bombing and save their neighbourhood, our heroes must penetrate the castle and face the two-headed king of giants.

episodes.name: The Demigod's Trial
episodes.overview: Today is the School Olympics! Malika wants our heroes to arrive at the stadium early. They meet Chloros, a frail looking demigod who has to prove to his father, Zeus, that he is a great athlete, in order to be admitted to Mount Olympus. Nate and Malika have an idea: they will compete against Chloros, and they'll let him win. But when Zeus finds out they deceived him, he unleashes his wrath on our heroes...

episodes.name: The Glitch
episodes.overview: Nate and Maurice have fun playing an augmented reality video game... until they accidentally release Zimbra, an evil artificial intelligence. The evil AI turns Maurice into a computer virus that can infect people with glitches! Our heroes have to prevent Zimbra from taking over the world, while dealing with Maurice who blames them!

episodes.name: The Munchkins
episodes.overview: This morning, Nate finds a tiny figurine in the street, not realizing that it's an important statue belonging to the King of the Tiny Tops. Furious that his statue was stolen, the King wages war against our heroes, who don't notice anything... until Tristan, a pacifist Tiny Top, asks for their help to make peace.

episodes.name: The Magicians Hat
episodes.overview: This morning, Nate and Malika meet Fluffy... a talking rabbit! He needs their help, because the magical world where he lives is in danger. Our heroes are sucked into a top hat, which contains this magical world! But soon, they discover that the responsible is none other than Jack Flash, the evil magician. Our heroes must thwart the wizard's plan before it's too late.

episodes.name: The Chromapix
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika discover that the neighborhood is being painted grey by a Necropix, a space creature who hates colors. Luckily, Carmine, a young superheroine Chromapix, arrives to stop it! Our heroes team up with Carmine to give the town its colors back, but they soon discover that she is hiding something from them...

episodes.name: The Gingerbread Family
episodes.overview: On the way to school, Nate and Malika run into tiny gingerbread creatures who are causing mayhem in town. As it happens, Yvan, their gingerbread friend, has been trying to bake himself a little brother. Unfortunately, magical baking can be dangerous and soon, Nate and Malika have to save Yvan from one of his creations!

episodes.name: The Alphabet Agency
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika cross paths with superheroine Miracle Girl when a secret agent arrives to arrest her! He pretends that it's only for a routine check, but our heroes smell a rat. They sneak into the Alphabet Agency and find out that she's the victim of a conspiracy.

episodes.name: The Wild Beasts
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika run into Maurice, who is half transformed into a hamster! They take him to their friend Pat, the werewolf vet, but they find her in the middle of a quarrel with Moro, the new leader of her werewolf pack. Moro's ready to do anything to force Pat to return to the wolves!

episodes.name: The Return of the Cuddly Toys
episodes.overview: On their way to school, Nate and Malika run into Brian, Santa's reindeer, who needs their help - Santa's in danger! Nate and Malika climb on Brian's back and fly off to the North Pole! They discover that the local cuddly toy gang have been manipulated by Stan, Santa's evil brother!

episodes.name: The Racecar
episodes.overview: Spoiler alert: Nate and Malika are as late as ever! On their daily journey to school they meet old and new friends and save their neighbourhood from absolute mayhem - but Principal Prudence still won't believe a word of their stories.

episodes.name: Inside Professor ToyBos
episodes.overview: Spoiler alert: Nate and Malika are as late as ever! On their daily journey to school they meet old and new friends and save their neighbourhood from absolute mayhem - but Principal Prudence still won't believe a word of their stories.

episodes.name: The Asteroid
episodes.overview: On their way to school, Nate and Malika make a quick stop at Professor Toybos's lab, which suddenly turns into a rocket, launches into space and lands on an asteroid! But Toybos's rival, Professor Bellding, is already on the asteroid to mine its precious mineral!

episodes.name: The Time-Travelers
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika run into Ascor, their friend from the future, who is pursuing an odious animal trafficker who travels back in time to capture specimens of extinct species! To stop him, Nate and Malika embark on a journey through time, but they accidentally create a time paradox!

episodes.name: The Nebulons
episodes.overview: On their way to school, Nate and Malika run into Billy, the shepherd of the City in the Sky, who is looking for his herd of Nebulons. These funny, cloudy sheep are the main source of water in the city, so he needs to bring them back as soon as possible - but Billy is captured by Carla, a bad cowgirl!

episodes.name: The Witch-Con
episodes.overview: By following a mysterious black cat in the park, Nate and Malika discover a secret convention for witches! But when someone steals scrolls and potions, the witches accuse Nate and Malika. Our heroes have to try and find the real culprit to clear their names!

episodes.name: The Kobolds
episodes.overview: On their way to school, Nate and Malika fall into a tunnel where they meet a group of Kobolds who are digging tunnels under the city. But when their giant pet mole starts to tunnel unusually fast, the town's foundations become unstable! Helped by the Kobolds, our heroes have to stop the mole!

episodes.name: The Superstars
episodes.overview: The town is hosting a talent contest. Nate and Malika run into Betty, a manager who dreams of becoming rich by having her dance duo win the contest. But when one of her teen stars suddenly drops out, Betty turns to Malika to replace her.

episodes.name: The Goblin Cousin
episodes.overview: On their way to school, Nate and Malika set out to find the source of a terrible stench spreading across town. It turns out to be Bubo, the cousin of Pimple, their goblin friend who lives in the sewers. With Pimple's help, our heroes try to convince Bubo to take a bath!

episodes.name: The Gold Crown
episodes.overview: At the museum, Nate and Malika try to prevent a thief from stealing the precious golden crown of an Inca emperor, but when Nate and the thief start turning everything they touch into gold, our heroes realise the crown was cursed!

episodes.name: The Scarecrow
episodes.overview: There is no sunrise! Nate and Malika encounter Noctis, small black creatures that gather in cities and plunge them into darkness. Fortunately, Jack the Scarecrow is here to chase them away!

episodes.name: The Banana Peel (1)
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika are trying to be on time for the last day of school, but Nate slips on a banana peel. That's nothing unusual, but the banana peel turns out to be alive and requests help getting its human form back.

episodes.name: The Banana Peel (2)
episodes.overview: Nate and Malika help Ben, the banana peel, get his powers back, but he betrays them. Instead of using his powers to become human, he takes revenge on humanity by turning the town into a magic realm! As magical creatures invade the city, our heroes try to help.
